<h2>Lightheadedness and Weakness</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms lightheadedness and weakness including Medication reaction or side-effect, Generalized anxiety disorder, and Fainting (vasovagal syncope).</p>
<p>There  are 33 conditions  associated with lightheadedness and weakness. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
